# LJM source repository (Layer 1)
#
# This .gitignore turns the vault root into a source-only git repository.
# Memory, Buffer, Archive, Metrics, and per-book ingestion manifests are
# all excluded — they live in the encrypted Layer-2 backup instead.
# See System/Backup.md for the full layered model.

# ── Memory and buffer state (encrypted-backup tier) ──────────────────────
Buffer/
Memory/
Archive/

# Metrics: only the audit trail belongs in source; the rest is local state.
Metrics/
!Metrics/.gitkeep

# Per-book ingestion manifests — track per-vault state, not source.
# The protocol README (Ingestion/_README.md) IS source and stays tracked.
Ingestion/manifest_*.md
Ingestion/INDEX.md

# ── Build artifacts and rebuildables ─────────────────────────────────────
/jm.exe
agent/jm
agent/jm.exe
agent/jm.test
agent/jm.test.exe
agent/johnnymnemonic
agent/johnnymnemonic.exe
agent/johnnymnemonic.test
agent/johnnymnemonic.test.exe
agent/coverage.out
agent/*.prof

# ── Editor and OS state ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/workspace-mobile.json
.obsidian/graph.json
.obsidian/cache
.obsidian/plugins/*/data.json

*.tmp
*.swp
*.swo
*~
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# ── Backup target directories (when sibling/in-tree) ─────────────────────
Backup/
backups/
*.age
*.meta.json

# ── Local-only Claude settings (machine-specific) ────────────────────────
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock

# ── Machine & tooling registry (real values; example is committed) ────────
System/machines.json
